## 🔌 CONNECT YOUR EXISTING ETL NODES HERE

**What to connect:**
1. Connect output from 'Fetch Apify Data' to your existing ETL pipeline
2. Keep ALL your existing Code nodes (Overview, Contact, Social, etc.)
3. Keep ALL your existing Merge nodes

**What to modify in your Code nodes:**
```javascript
// At the top of EACH Code node, add:
const executionId = $('Store Execution ID').first().json.execution_id;

// In your return statement, add execution_id:
return items.map(item => {
  return {
    json: {
      execution_id: executionId,  // ADD THIS
      // ... rest of your existing fields
    }
  };
});
```

**Then connect your final merged output to 'Combine Business Data' node below.**

